This dataset contains QSIRecon (version 1.0.1) derivatives for the PAFIN dataset (https://openneuro.org/datasets/ds006131), derived from QSIPrep outputs (https://openneuro.org/datasets/ds006182).

The command used is:

```
qsirecon \
    /data/qsiprep \
    /data/qsirecon \
    participant \
    --output-resolution 1.7 \
    --recon-spec /code/recon_spec.yml \
    --report-output-level session  
```
